name: All Wrapped Up (V)
Lore: 'A capture cable is a quick and effective way for bounty hunters to suddenly snare their target.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Double Back is a Used Interrupt. Once per turn, may take Bounty into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If present, your bounty hunter may capture a character opponent just forfeited at same site. Whenever you collect a bounty, may place that Effect out of play to take a retrieved card into hand. (Immune to Alter.)',
